{"tid":445763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗港獨，我地有得揀咩？","createTime":"2017-10-23T16:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T18:38:26.000Z","uid":104096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"889c5d49929069a779af52cc6083cbc73794c8f2","tid":445763,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:06:58.000Z","msg":"基本法無用，中共唔會民主化，大陸人唔會番大陸<br />\n民主唔會從個天跌落嚟<br />\n咁除咗港獨仲有咩自救方法姐？<br />\n姑勿論港獨可唔可行，我只係見到嘅一方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然你可以駁我港獨同中共民主化一樣唔會放俾你<br />\n咁所以流血同革命少不免。<br />\n<br />\n講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cf991ad06ea12df72593dc4a058ce852366518","tid":445763,"uid":80535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"港獨係唯一路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但成堆港豬馬照跑舞照跳 Wfc"},{"pid":"354ef868ae411edebecc50e06cd58a4caa4085a0","tid":445763,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec318531ddcef185919ef3806938ba4cb73f3f6","tid":445763,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港獨係唯一路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但成堆港豬馬照跑舞照跳 Wfc</blockquote><br />\n坦白講，有幾多個香港人會諗前途問題<br />\n屌我真係覺得香港人好撚戇鳩<br />\n2047一定埋單計數，仲可以點避"},{"pid":"acb7839c1685a368ccedede8a80488a2bf0127b6","tid":445763,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冚家剷最後一國一制我地全部都係同一命運"},{"pid":"833e1464a58e483c34cc8673b90256f282ddddd7","tid":445763,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"可行性我唔理，但係係我唯一接受既出路"},{"pid":"4747e4346628e3e450b851ba